{"tid":2300747,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【7,000萬分紅案】周星馳再臨法庭：高院應該裝修吓","createTime":"2020-11-25T18:53:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-27T23:58:36.000Z","uid":240362,"like":81,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"c8e576e3ec36d6ad51cd2e779018b9f2545bc60a","tid":2300747,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T18:53:34.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】本案審訊多日，男主角周星馳昨終出庭作供，吸引大批記者一早霸位採訪。休庭期間上演一幕疑似女影迷送上兩個李小龍首辦模型打氣，令人想起食神中女學生送花情節。官司纏身的星爺不忘搞笑，見有記者投以羡慕目光，打趣說：「送個畀你？」又反問追訪記者「最近忙啲咩」。自言並非首次到訪法庭的他不諱言高等法院比較舊：「應該裝修吓啦。」<br />\n<br />\n周星馳昨早9時已抵達高院，但未有如于文鳳或其他證人般由大樓噴水池正門出入，令一眾守候記者向隅。開庭前，有記者邀請星爺到法院外拍照，他稱：「今日無化妝⋯⋯不如喺呢度（影）？」又透露非首次到法庭，懷着平常心作證，並不緊張。問他覺得法庭如何，有律師說「比較舊啲啦」，他同意道：「應該裝修吓啦。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201126/5QPLJGTIYZC6TNOGV7MI5CCBBA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201126%2F5QPLJGTIYZC6TNOGV7MI5CCBBA%2F&d=Z5fxCpLMP6GgpQ63MmTuwqy4iG8TIfC1p449sO1N5Ck%3D&h=ea00060c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201126%2F5QPLJGTIYZC6TNOGV7MI5CCBBA%2F&h=bc768b8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201126/5QPLJGTIYZC6TNOGV7MI5CCBBA/</a>"},{"pid":"e6a0c32c4478fb9bb8c5fcf6c6b9684512eae0ce","tid":2300747,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T18:55:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"040be0d8049bd79522ad355ca06915bd6ebbb4e2","tid":2300747,"uid":251732,"like":56,"dislike":0,"score":56,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T18:59:09.000Z","msg":"周星星犯咗國安法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2da364d1bf4fa3b4b2085443d7fa21006ca5e246","tid":2300747,"uid":79117,"like":105,"dislike":1,"score":104,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T19:00:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cf7c65f05a7618566f58dcd30ee8581012f1e7d9","tid":2300747,"uid":290314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0